captions.text:
Put on a full metal alchemist suit of armor
and grab your poke ball mug because I’m
Jake and this is Game Lut 31!

Don a Light up Samus Helmet before exploring
the solar system in your kerbel space ship

that you can 3d print at Euclid. If you’d
rather achieve lightspeed fire up a Millennium

Falcom shaped custom gaming pc, just be sure
you never tell me the odds.

And bring along a gentleman caller clap trap
action figure? At least then you’d have

someone to play the Street Fighter Card game
with, don’t worry I’m Shoryuken beat him.

But to beat this Queen of Blades Costume from
starcraft you’ll need something solid…..

like a Replica of Raidan's sword from Metal
Gear Rising: Revengence.

All this adventuring has probably tired you
out, why don’t you grab a Tetris Pillow,

wrap yourself in a Pixel Nostalgia duvet,
and have a dark knight in your Batman Bed.
Justice is so comfy.

Ahh!! Whats that sound!? Oh it’s just my
super mario alarm clock going off, You can’t

tell me to get out of bed you’re not my
REAL Octodad…t-shirt.

Fine I guess we can get out of bed and look
at the amazing prints Stephen Dye

Now open up your TARDIS Jewelry box, don’t
worry it’s bigger on the inside…and grab

your zora sapphire ring. Before going out
you’ll need that Thor’s Hammer Purse and
one of these amazon Spiderman Dresses.

Oops, looks like you don’t have any rupees
in your LoZ Wallet, you should stay in tonight,

throw on a Joker Onesies and bake some cookies
with an adventure time rolling pin. Just make

sure you have all of the ingredients in your
Gameboy Decals covered fridge.

YOU SHALL NOT PASS…. Lord of the Rings Salt
and Pepper Shakers over these cookies and

pour some milk in an Attack on Titan Stein.
Then wind down by playing on the Analogue

NT, an NES console built from a solid block
of aluminum that outputs NES games in HD.

If the NES is too slow for you then you could
always power up a Sonic painted Sega Genesis.

What’s this? A Totoro Bath Set? This will
go perfect with my 16 bit Game controller

welcome mat, Now I finally have something
to wipe my Mega Man sneakers on, puuuuurrrfect

Solid Gold Bane Cat! What are you doing here?
Stay away from my Batman Arkham Action Figure

Set! Shoo! Shoo! Go play with that Ultron
Prime Figurine, don’t worry I’m sure nothing

bad will happen. Better put on a Cubone Mask
just in case.

But just in case put on a Cubone mask and
check out these Nintendo Games re-imagined
as the covers of Pulp Novels.
